  "text": "It follows that, as in k-FAST where it was enough to consider directed triangles as conflict, we can restrict our attention to conflicts on sets of four leaves. Hereafter, the term of conflict is only used on set of four leaves. Our kernelization algorithm uses the following rule from [CITATION_1] .",
